The paper discusses the use of unsupervised strategies for particle sorting in single-particle cryo-EM, which involves image processing and machine learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
